Class MsdxRecord.Builder

java.lang.Object
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.MsdxContainer.Builder<java.lang.Object>
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.objectModel.MsdxRecord.Builder
Enclosing class:
MsdxRecord
public static class MsdxRecord.Builder
extends MsdxContainer.Builder<java.lang.Object>
This class enables building a Record item by item. It also permits copying one or more items from another Container and for removing unnecessary copies. When the Record is built, it validates the items against the Schema. You can also build a Record with all null items, which is useful when an Operator needs to return a Record with missing items.
